snippet.title: How Miranda Lambert Really Feels About Gwen Stefani
snippet.description:
For a few years, Blake Shelton and Miranda Lambert were one of the hottest couples in the country music scene, but it all came crashing down in 2015 when the two singers announced they were divorcing. Not long after, Shelton began dating another singer: former No Doubt frontwoman and fellow coach on "The Voice," Gwen Stefani.

With Shelton quickly in another high-profile relationship, plenty of fans had opinions and questions, with many wondering how Lambert felt about the whole thing. Obviously, no one is going to be thrilled about a divorce, but let’s take a look at how Miranda Lambert really feels about Gwen Stefani.
